{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B37ThemeTextInputComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for input text component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text input component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMaxWidth: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._3000 }","","        override var spacePaddingBlockDefault: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSmall }","","        override var colorBorderEnabled: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthMedium}","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: TextInputComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color, space and _ semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}]}]}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTextInputComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent09TextInputB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextinputcomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:dimensions:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/TextInputComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/O